  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK595">
<l>veḷḷat taṉaiya malarnīṭṭa māntartam </l>
<l>muḷḷat taṉaiya tuyarvu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The stalks of water-flowers are proportionate to the depth of water; so is men's greatness proportionate to their minds.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
